data.description: You do not want to miss this beautiful 5 bedroom, 3 bath home located in The Lakes of Bailey Ranch in Owasso. This home features an open floor plan with wood floors, outdoor entertainment, pergola, and an extended covered patio that overlooks a gorgeous pond! This home also boasts a large, fully floored walk-in attic, 5 car garage, and an indoor storm shelter. Primary suite overlooks pond featuring a large walk-in closet with abundant storage, and spa like bathroom with double sinks, soaking tub, separate walk-in shower, and private water closet. A definite must see!
